 {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );
            }
            {
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();
                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

            {
				string[] colors =
				{
					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            }

                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();

                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);

					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();

					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {

                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod

                watch.Start();
                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

            {
				string[] colors =
				{
					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);

					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );
            }

                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);

                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {

                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

                watch.Start();
                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

            {
				string[] colors =
				{
					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);

					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );
            }

                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);

                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {

                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

                watch.Start();
                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

            {
				string[] colors =
				{
					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);

					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );
            }

                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

                watch.Start();
                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

            {
				string[] colors =
				{
					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);

					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );
            }

                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

                watch.Start();
                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

            {
				string[] colors =
				{
					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {

					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );
            }

                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

                watch.Start();
                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

            {
				string[] colors =
				{
					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod

                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);

                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);

                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);

                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

                watch.Start();
                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

            {
				string[] colors =
				{
					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod

					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            }

                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);

                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );

                watch.Start();
                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

            {
				string[] colors =
				{
					"1. Red",
					"2. Green",
					"3. Blue",
					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod

					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);

                Parallel.For(0, 201, i =>
                {
                    Get();
                    Console.WriteLine(i+" ");
                    //Console.WriteLine("Thread Id= {1}", Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
            }

					"4. Yellow",
					"5. White",
					"6. Black",
					"7. Violet",
					"8. Brown",
					"9. Orange",
					"10. Pink"
				};
               
                watch = new Stopwatch();
                watch.Start();


                Parallel.ForEach(colors, color =>
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("{0}, Thread Id= {1}", color, Thread.CurrentThread.ManagedThreadId);
                    Thread.Sleep(30);
                });
                watch.Stop();
                // Write result
                Console.WriteLine("Parallel Time elapsed: {0}", watch.Elapsed.TotalSeconds);
                
            } {
                Parallel.Invoke(
                    ()=>AnyMethod,
                    ()=>AnyMethod
                    );
